sequenceDiagram
    actor Guest
    participant FE as Frontend (Vercel)
    participant API as Elysia API (Railway)
    participant Redis
    participant Worker
    participant Whisper as Whisper :8000
    participant Groq as Groq Cloud API
    participant Ollama as Ollama (fallback)
    participant PG as PostgreSQL
    actor Staff

    Guest->>FE: Tap-to-record voice (any language)
    FE->>API: POST /api/requests/voice (base64 audio)
    API->>PG: INSERT request (queued)
    API->>Redis: Enqueue → transcription (base64 payload)
    API-->>FE: { request_id }
    FE->>API: Opens SSE stream

    Redis->>Worker: Dequeue transcription
    Worker->>Whisper: POST /transcribe (base64 audio)
    Whisper-->>Worker: { text, lang, confidence }
    Worker->>PG: INSERT transcription
    Worker->>Redis: Publish status update
    API-->>FE: "Transcribed ✓"

    Worker->>Redis: Enqueue → classification
    Redis->>Worker: Dequeue classification
    Worker->>Groq: POST /chat/completions (~500ms)
    alt Groq unavailable (circuit breaker)
        Worker->>Ollama: POST /api/generate (fallback)
    end
    Groq-->>Worker: { department, urgency, summary }
    Worker->>PG: INSERT classification + workflow
    Worker->>Redis: Publish to staff channels
    API-->>FE: "Routed to Maintenance ✓"

    Redis-->>API: Pub/sub event
    API->>Staff: WebSocket push (new workflow card)
    Staff->>API: POST /workflows/:id/claim
    API->>Redis: Publish update
    API-->>FE: "Juan is on the way"
